metadata.description:
they say hard work pays off, so i can't wait.

I work day 'n night, wake up real early and stay up real late.

Destined for greatness, I can taste it. Made sure not to fall for the bait.

 My mama always told me I was going to be a star one day, it must be fate.

I swear it feels different when you make it out of nothing, there's no debate.
